data.description: TONS OF POTENTIAL & EQUITY!!! Located in a charming, well desired neighborhood right outside La Plata, this beautiful 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home is a true gem. Serving as the former Model Home for the Chapel Point Woods Community, it exudes elegance and comfort at every turn.   Step inside to discover a spacious interior featuring 9' ceilings and luxurious LVP flooring throughout. Crown molding adds a touch of sophistication to the open layout, which includes a well-appointed kitchen complete with a pantry and ample counter space. The inviting family room is highlighted by a cozy wood-burning fireplace, perfect for gatherings on chilly evenings.  Entertain guests in the formal living and dining rooms, or retreat to the grand master suite boasting his and hers walk-in closets and a private bathroom with double sinks, a deep soaking tub, and a separate shower. Huge additional bedrooms also offers large closets, ensuring everyone has plenty of storage space.  Outside, you'll find an attached 2-car garage, a welcoming front porch, and a large deck ideal for outdoor dining and relaxation. Enjoy endless summer fun in the 32' x 16' above-ground saltwater pool. Multiple storage sheds provide room for all your outdoor equipment, while recent upgrades including a new roof, HVAC system, hot water heater, Anderson windows, and outdoor solar motion lighting offer peace of mind and modern convenience.  Conveniently located near shopping, restaurants, and commuter routes to Washington DC, Andrews AFB, and NOVA, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and style. Don't miss your chance to make this exquisite property your own!
